<section id="about-page" class="pt-70 pb-110">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-5">
                <div class="section-title mt-50">
                    <h5>About us</h5>
                    <h2>Welcome to IHMS </h2>
                </div> <!-- section title -->
                <div class="about-cont">
                    <p>
                        One of the core functionalities of the system is the management of patient records. It provides a centralized database where all relevant patient information, including medical history, diagnoses, and treatment plans, can be stored and accessed securely. This ensures quick and accurate retrieval of patient data, enabling healthcare providers to make well-informed decisions and deliver personalized care.
                        Data security and privacy are of paramount importance in the healthcare industry. The Interior Hospital Management System incorporates robust security measures to safeguard sensitive patient information. Access controls, encryption, and regular data backups are implemented to protect data integrity and confidentiality.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div> <!-- about cont -->
            <div class="col-lg-7">
                <div class="about-image mt-50">
                    <img src="~/IndexAssets/images/about/about-2.jpg" alt="About">
                </div>  <!-- about imag -->
            </div>
        </div> <!-- row -->
        <div class="about-items pt-60">
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-10">
                    <div class="about-singel-items mt-30">
                        <span>01</span>
                        <h4>Why Choose us</h4>
                        <p>Because of our hospital focuses on the individual needs and preferences of our patients. We strive to create a compassionate and comfortable environment, promoting trust and open communication.</p>
                    </div> <!-- about singel -->
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-10">
                    <div class="about-singel-items mt-30">
                        <span>02</span>
                        <h4>Our Mission</h4>
                        <p>Our mission is to promote wellness, provide compassionate care, and enhance the quality of life for our patients.With a commitment to excellence, our mission is to be the trusted choice for superior healthcare services in our region.</p>
                    </div> <!-- about singel -->
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-10">
                    <div class="about-singel-items mt-30">
                        <span>03</span>
                        <h4>Our vision</h4>
                        <p>
                            Our vision is to be a leading healthcare provider, delivering exceptional medical services and compassionate care to our community.
                            We strive to enhance the well-being of individuals and families by promoting a culture of health and wellness.
                        </p>
                    </div> <!-- about singel -->
                </div>
            </div> <!-- row -->
        </div> <!-- about items -->
    </div> <!-- container -->
</section>
